            <li class="sel"><a href="my-profile.html">My Profile</a></li>
            <li><a href="change-password.html">Change Password</a></li>
            <li><a href="add-food-listing.html">Add a food listing</a></li>
            <li><a href="add-event.html">Add an event</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right-box-border">
        <div class="right-box-main">
          <div class="inner-left-right-side-title">Latest Events</div>
          <br />
          August 10, 2011 – Arlington Farmers Market
